  "slug": "phat-phonk-by-dadabots",
  "title": "Phat Phonk by Dadabots",
  "summary": "<p>Gluttony</p>\n<p>The artist duo Dadabots has been using artificial intelligence to create music since 2012. What initially began with music remix bots evolved into a sprawling practice, including 24/7 livestreams of newly generated music across multiple genres. Having generated millions of hours of music, the duo has created more music than could ever possibly be created by a completely human band. In <em>Phat Phonk</em>, the pair turns the dial to Phonk, the storied hip-hop subgenre which saw a revival on TikTok in 2020. Separated into 50 fragments, <em>Phat Phonk</em> is a mixtape with indulgent driving bass and aggressive percussion—a staple of the genre. Each artwork shows a preview of the full sound, but must be downloaded in order to be heard in their entirety. Despite their relatively short runtime, each fragment takes up between 89GB-29TB of hardware space, making the entire 25-minute mixtape incredibly resource-intensive for a listener to assemble.</p>\n<p><em>Phat Phonk</em> is delivered to listeners with the following warning from the artist:<br>((SURGEON GENERAL WARNING)) HAZARDOUS GORGING LEADS TO BLOAT, POSSIBLE MALFUNCTION. REMAIN DILIGENT.</p>\n<p>DADABOTS MIXTAPE W/ BEATS UNAPOLOGETICLY PHAT, AIRWAVES SMOTHERED W/ IRREVERENT COLOSSAL PRESENCE. HEAVY. SUBMERGED 29HZ BASSLINES MONSTROUSLY SATURATED. SWELLS BEYOND CONFINES. DEVOURS EVERY FREQUENCY UNTIL SPECTRUM IS SUMPTUOUS INDULGENT RUMBLE.</p>\n<p>ONE MIXTAPE. TEN TRACKS. HIDING IN PIECES. CUT, CHOPPED &amp; CHEWED. SERVED DOUBLE WRAPPED PROSCIUTTO EN CROÛTE.</p>\n<p>BEWARE: SIZE EXPANDS RAPIDLY ONCE CONSUMED.</p>\n",
